Bomu Hunting Reserve (French: Domaine de Chasse Bomu) bụ ebe ịchụnta (IUCN Category II) na Democratic Republic of the Congo
Ogige ahụ kpuchiri mpaghara nke 4,125.6 km2
Osimiri Mbomou dị n'ebe ugwu, nke na-eme ka ókèala ya na Central African Republic
Ọ na-ejikọta Bili-Uere Hunting Reserve n'ebe ndịda.
